    <p>
      By using oriz.in or any <code>*.oriz.in</code> site, you agree to these terms. They are
      short on purpose.
    </p>

    <h2>Use the sites lawfully</h2>
    <p>
      Don't try to break the sites, scrape them at abusive rates, or use them to harass others.
      Account takeover, copyright infringement, and any activity prohibited under Indian law are
      forbidden.
    </p>

    <h2>Content is provided as-is</h2>
    <p>
      Calculators, summaries, and tools on oriz are provided for information and convenience only.
      They are not professional advice. Verify anything before relying on it. See the full
      <a href="/legal/disclaimer/">disclaimer</a>.
    </p>

